{"tid":311372,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"網絡時代變遷","createTime":"2017-07-06T14:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T17:02:49.000Z","uid":127075,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95d9366de1e8d3b5c055df929221ab3529e98771","tid":311372,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人同我一樣 好懷念icq msn qooza blog 畫板online game 同早期facebook年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nicq blog直頭冇人用 facebook而家game又廢 <br />\n自從身邊朋友轉曬IG 冇再更新fb 令到自己開FB已經冇左目標<br />\n以前facebook 就算係好垃圾既開心寶貝都可以同班FD有個話題玩得好開心 <br />\n各種對答洗版 無無聊聊坐係屋企 撩班朋友傾計<br />\n而家ig見到有post 對答都係一句起兩句止 就再沒有下文<br />\nmsn d遊戲簡直世界級 完全能夠增進雙方感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmsn聽咩歌 睇咩片又可以比人知 鍾意又可以有狀態<br />\n頭像只係見到卡通都可以傾得好開心<br />\n而家頭像唔係人樣生得唔靚既話根本冇人會理 <br />\n至於online game都可以話識到朋友 而家玩完就算<br />\n身邊朋友由有到冇 轉whatsapp ig後就再冇聯絡<br />\n只有鍵盤與鍵盤之間才可以對答如流<br />\n電話同電話跟本只有已讀 唔會再有離線<br />\n問世間試問仲有邊一款社交平台係可以好似以前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時候睇返以前facebook 對答真係另有一翻風味<br />\n究竟係時代變遷 定係現實其實就係咁<br />\n人係咪又一定要隨波逐流 先至可以埋到堆呢?<br />\nskype whatsapp ig 我屌曬你地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  msn settings NO.1<br />\n<br />\n可能字多左少少,排版又唔算太好<br />\n但我只係有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鍵盤打字真係好爽 手機過多1千幾百年都唔會比人上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae63073a041fb2765bbb32ae4cf07f50cec5a06","tid":311372,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:28:01.000Z","msg":"之前SD SMS溝通要問下係咪同台<br />\nXG睇D 古時MK妹打既文<br />\nMSN 震人<br />\n00後唔會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00977524a14e32f17d2fec2d0140366015197133","tid":311372,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:30:31.000Z","msg":"MSN可以玩小遊戲"},{"pid":"99aeb92b7f301c6d4eb383804281ab4e37bbb978","tid":311372,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前SD SMS溝通要問下係咪同台<br />\nXG睇D 古時MK妹打既文<br />\nMSN 震人<br />\n00後唔會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n00後得IG LINE 個堆玩 完全唔同feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nfacebook以前都有follow女神個種衝動 <br />\nig set左私隱唔識既真係唔會襟落去<br />\n結果而家連ig開黎都冇意思"},{"pid":"5bf447b4a449557a3f1add837daaa0cb52fa4a5a","tid":311372,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>MSN可以玩小遊戲</blockquote><br />\n保齡 踩地雷 都好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家陣已經玩唔返"},{"pid":"2a45816194d7beda63ffa31b9eb1269b15f4b348","tid":311372,"uid":5725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"小學個留言板真係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   留埋d 小學雞野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有得睇返一定好好笑"},{"pid":"925e04c1a18e2c2fd54e000909341fd5249bd6cc","tid":311372,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:56:39.000Z","msg":"icq都已經算係轉折期出現既產物<br />\n<br />\n係icq前仲有chatroom同internet phone"},{"pid":"0db163eb90313f7dc3ead971d035168590f82d28","tid":311372,"uid":127075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>icq都已經算係轉折期出現既產物<br />\n<br />\n係icq前仲有chatroom同internet phone</blockquote><br />\n都係個類好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  手機chat已經係另一個世界黎<br />\n以前D人鍾意煲電話粥 而家whatapp傾曬"},{"pid":"3d8a3046f7c085965d0bd082a7815149ac3b2d67","tid":311372,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{